      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ATOMIC PRINCE (7) was well fancied but drifted back before winding up with a late dash home to place, 2.25 lengths from the winner (20.02) at this track in Maiden. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Deserves serious consideration. TIP TOP TAMMY (1) is yet to break through in 12 starts but has run a number of placings. Is better than last start when out of the placings, finishing fifth (19.62) at Q Straight. Strong form has emerged from her last run. Bold showing expected. WALLOON ROCKET (2) unfancied latest but hit the ground running and gave a sight, holding on for a minor placing (20.20) at this track in a Maiden over 352m. Can feature again. HARA'S ROCKY (3) is by Rejuvenate out of Hara's Indi making debut. Expected to produce a bold debut.",
